tainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782822705996,"wordCount":501},{"articleId":"2dgmaf6","headline":"Grammy-Winning DJ Fred Again Announces First-Ever Shows in Delhi, Mumbai and Bengaluru","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fgrammy-winning-dj-fred-again-announces-first-ever-shows-in-delhi-mumbai-and-bengaluru-articleshow-2dgmaf6","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kvwnq3jxtcze05c60wha0zah\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--65--1782299987549.png","publishedDate":1782300943932,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EBritish electronic music sensation Fred Again.. has officially announced his long-awaited India debut with a three-city tour in December 2026. The Grammy-winning producer will perform in Delhi NCR, Mumbai and Bengaluru, marking his first-ever concerts in the country.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 24 2026, 05:05 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782300943937,"wordCount":533},{"articleId":"zfrgdy1","headline":"Why Amazon Backed Out of Sam Altman Film 'Artificial' Despite Near-Completion","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fwhy-amazon-backed-out-of-sam-altman-film-artificial-despite-near-completion-articleshow-zfrgdy1","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kvqm3hvht07p8c79hrw73hpy\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--61--1782130526065.png","publishedDate":1782132258521,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EAmazon MGM Studios has dropped Luca Guadagnino's nearly completed Sam Altman biopic 'Artificial' following its $50 billion OpenAI partnership. Here's what happened, why the project was shelved, and what comes next.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 22 2026, 06:14 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782132258525,"wordCount":519},{"articleId":"kre64cs","headline":"Christopher Nolan, Matt Damon and Tom Holland to Visit India for 'The Odyssey' Premiere","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fchristopher-nolan-matt-damon-and-tom-holland-to-visit-india-for-the-odyssey-premiere-articleshow-kre64cs","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kvd80szzed4j031hz6709dgr\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--58--1781782308863.png","publishedDate":1781784461537,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EHollywood visionary Christopher Nolan is set to make history by bringing superstars Matt Damon and Tom Holland to Mumbai for the highly anticipated grand Indian premiere of his IMAX epic 'The Odyssey.'\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 18 2026, 05:37 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1781845375095,"wordCount":529},{"articleId":"5qx0cvt","headline":"Michael Jackson Biopic 'Michael' Becomes Highest-Grossing Music Biopic Ever, Beats 'Bohemian Rhapsody'","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fmichael-surpasses-bohemian-rhapsody-at-global-box-office-nears-historic-1-billion-dollar-mark-articleshow-5qx0cvt","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kv56cxc790xjf1h310tmhbwr\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--51--1781512172935.png","publishedDate":1781519720836,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EMichael Jackson biopic 'Michael' has overtaken 'Bohemian Rhapsody' to become the highest-grossing music biopic of all time, with worldwide earnings nearing the $1 billion mark.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 15 2026, 04:05 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1781519720840,"wordCount":605},{"articleId":"645vmd5","headline":"Lionel Messi Joins Tom Holland in 'Spider-Man: Brand New Day' Promo","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Flionel-messi-joins-tom-holland-in-spider-man-brand-new-day-promo-articleshow-645vmd5","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kwenj721twtmvzv6wcfffbj0\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--72--1782903807040.png","publishedDate":1782904072196,"description":"\u003Cp\u003ELionel Messi's surprise appearance alongside Tom Holland in a 'Spider-Man: Brand New Day' promotional video has become one of 2026's biggest viral entertainment moments. The unexpected crossover is boosting anticipation for the Marvel film, which arrives in theaters on 31st July, with Tom Holland returning as Peter Parker.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jul 01 2026, 04:37 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782904072201,"wordCount":636},{"articleId":"gq57146","headline":"Amid 'MobLand' Controversy, Tom Hardy Announces 'Czarface Meets Frankie Pulitzer' Rap Album","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Famid-mobland-controversy-tom-hardy-announces-czarface-meets-frankie-pulitzer-rap-album-articleshow-gq57146","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kw9p6m7bw5xcd2cetzj6bny0\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--70--1782736703723.png","publishedDate":1782737564307,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EHollywood star Tom Hardy makes a surprise return to his underground hip-hop roots, announcing an all-star collaborative rap album with Czarface and Busta Rhymes scheduled for an August release.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 29 2026, 06:22 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782737564312,"wordCount":632},{"articleId":"kpw8psd","headline":"After 9 Years, Paul Wesley & Nina Dobrev Are Back Together for Hulu's 'You Deserve to Know'","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fafter-9-years-paul-wesley-and-nina-dobrev-are-back-together-for-hulu-you-deserve-to-know-articleshow-kpw8psd","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kw9nnbrwpn84k2wpzp3ep65t\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--69--1782736138012.png","publishedDate":1782736160361,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EPaul Wesley and Nina Dobrev are reuniting as both stars and executive producers for Hulu's 'You Deserve to Know,' based on Aggie Blum Thompson's bestselling 2025 novel. The long-awaited collaboration marks their first major scripted project together since 'The Vampire Diaries' ended in 2017.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 29 2026, 05:59 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782736160365,"wordCount":779},{"articleId":"ikry26m","headline":"Sam Smith Announces 'Hazel Eyes': Inside the Grammy Winner's First Album in Three Years","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fafter-years-of-global-success-sam-smith-returns-with-intimate-new-album-hazel-eyes-articleshow-ikry26m","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kvz3kpsbn2fat5g8hdtz25th\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--67--1782381665067.png","publishedDate":1782386568854,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EGrammy-winning singer-songwriter Sam Smith is returning with their fifth studio album, 'Hazel Eyes,' due out on 21st August. The announcement comes with the release of the emotional lead single 'My Guy,' a song inspired by love, personal growth, and life in New York City.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 25 2026, 04:52 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782386568858,"wordCount":545},{"articleId":"61o4kkc","headline":"Liam Payne's 9-Year-Old Son Bear Set to Inherit $28 Million Following Singer's Death","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fcourt-rules-liam-paynes-son-bear-will-inherit-entire-28-million-dollars-estate-articleshow-61o4kkc","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kvsz6zaw1ytsnvm9drzp2s3f\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--63--1782209281372.png","publishedDate":1782214007402,"description":"\u003Cp\u003ENearly two years after Liam Payne's tragic death, new court documents have confirmed that his son Bear will inherit the singer's entire estate. The ruling also clarifies how the fortune will be managed until Bear reaches adulthood.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 23 2026, 04:56 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782214007405,"wordCount":464},{"articleId":"05pqf67","headline":"Olivia Rodrigo's 'You Seem Pretty Sad' Debuts at No. 1, Overtakes Drake's 2026 Record","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Folivia-rodrigo-extends-winning-streak-with-third-consecutive-no-1-album-on-billboard-200-articleshow-05pqf67","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kvqprhgj1x8tdjhc8s1j4sax\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--62--1782133310993.png","publishedDate":1782134105958,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EOlivia Rodrigo has scored the biggest solo album debut of 2026, overtaking Drake and earning her third consecutive No. 1 album on the Billboard 200. The achievement further cements her status as one of music’s most successful young stars.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 22 2026, 06:45 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782134105964,"wordCount":544},{"articleId":"95tnfxn","headline":"Xperience Sessions With HRVY","link":"\u002Fvideos\u002Fxperience-sessions-with-hrvy-11735438","type":"VIDEO","imageURL":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2026\u002F04\u002F17\u002Funtitled-design-21-2026-04-17-11-01-58.png","videoURL":"https:\u002F\u002Fyoutu.be\u002FPSZLSyn9ma4?si=eyrYg0eZuZ7kVxVa","publishedDate":1776404056169,"description":"Join HRVY on the latest Xperience Sessions as he sits down with RJ Ayesha to discuss his journey and new single, 'Lie to Me.' Dive into this exclusive conversation about his raw, honest transition into his latest musical chapter.","stats":"00:00","readableDate":"Apr 17 2026, 11:04 AM IST","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Videos","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fvideos","updatedAt":1776404056169},{"articleId":"btutm8i","headline":"Xperience Sessions With Richard Dudley","link":"\u002Fvideos\u002Fxperience-sessions-with-richard-dudley-11730798","type":"VIDEO","imageURL":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2026\u002F04\u002F16\u002Funtitled-design-20-2026-04-16-10-54-58.png","videoURL":"https:\u002F\u002Fyoutu.be\u002FUyhJwkn1gfc?si=Q064zka59m7Esb9C","publishedDate":1776317191445,"description":"The Xperience Sessions spotlighted music artist Richard Dudley of Moksha All Stars, who later took the stage at Hard Rock Cafe, Whitefield, Bengaluru on 28th March, delivering a mesmerizing live performance. ","stats":"00:00","readableDate":"Apr 16 2026, 10:56 AM IST","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Videos","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Fvideos","updatedAt":1776317191445},{"articleId":"ngz6gh2","headline":"Xperience Sessions With Peter and Aruvian","link":"\u002Foriginals\u002Foriginals-music-video\u002Fxperience-sessions-with-peter-and-aruvian-11368117","type":"VIDEO","imageURL":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2026\u002F03\u002F27\u002Fharry-po-2026-03-27t160402-2026-03-27-16-04-25.png","videoURL":"https:\u002F\u002Fyoutu.be\u002FVw4tfSsqO1Y?si=MIvgHH3y0oK6qvW3","publishedDate":1774607738677,"description":"RJ Simona recently sat down with Peter and Aruvian for an engaging conversation about the much-anticipated Acoustic Alchemy evening set to take place on 28th March at The Koramangala Club.","stats":"00:00","readableDate":"Mar 27 2026, 04:05 PM IST","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Videos","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Foriginals\u002Foriginals-music-video","updatedAt":1774607738677},{"articleId":"6fexcr4","headline":"Xperience Sessions With Vieux Farka Touré","link":"\u002Foriginals\u002Foriginals-music-video\u002Fxperience-sessions-with-vieux-farka-touré-11111543","type":"VIDEO","imageURL":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2026\u002F02\u002F16\u002Fharry-po-2026-02-16t-2026-02-16-17-05-19.png","videoURL":"https:\u002F\u002Fyoutu.be\u002Fdc9gSiCqIew?si=DtB1c0tc-JNi5Mow","publishedDate":1771241758201,"description":"The Xperience Sessions featured music artist Vieux Farka Touré, who delivered a captivating live performance at The Sixth Sense on 15th February, bringing an unforgettable evening of music to Bengaluru.","stats":"00:00","readableDate":"Feb 16 2026, 05:05 PM IST","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Videos","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"categoryUrl":"\u002Foriginals\u002Foriginals-music-video","updatedAt":1771241758201}]}},"sectionConfig":"","sectionsData":"","budgetHeadline":"","trendingTopic":"","budgetLBData":"","lbArticalData":"","bannerVal":0,"electionLBData":"","starCandidate":""},"articleshow":{"data":{"firstArticle":{"id":"mlzihg3","categoryId":140048,"categoryName":"Pop News","seo":{"keywords":["Kate Hudson","Almost Famous","Penny Lane"],"newsKeywords":["Kate Hudson","Almost Famous","Penny Lane"],"title":"Kate Hudson Reveals How She Fought to Play Penny Lane in 'Almost Famous'","description":"Pop News | Kate Hudson recalls nearly being cast in the small role of Anita in 'Almost Famous,' but convinced Cameron Crowe to give her a chance at Penny Lane. The Oscar‑nominated performance became her breakout at 19. ","canonical":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fkate-hudson-reveals-how-she-fought-to-play-penny-lane-in-almost-famous-10466008","ogTitle":"Kate Hudson Reveals How She Fought to Play Penny Lane in 'Almost Famous'","ogDescription":"In a recent interview marking Almost Famous's 25th anniversary, Kate Hudson shared she was originally cast as Anita before persuading director Cameron Crowe to let her audition for Penny Lane.","ogImage":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F09\u002F15\u002Funtitled-design-2025-09-15-15-00-38.png","noindex":false},"editorHTML":"\u003Cp\u003ECameron Crowe's semi-autobiographical coming-of-age picture, 'Almost Famous,'&nbsp;was released on the big screen in the 2000s. Billy Crudup played the band's charismatic lead, Russell Hammond; While, Frances McDormand and Jason Lee were supporting parts; Patrick Fugit played the teenage journalist William Miller, who tours with the 1970s rock group Stillwater; and a young Kate Hudson played Penny Lane, a captivating groupie who serves as the story's muse and emotional fulcrum.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cdiv type=\"dfp\" position=1\u003EAd1\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic-gi.asianetnews.com\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fpost_attachments\u002Fcinemaexpress\u002F2025-09-14\u002Fzneid6sc\u002FKate-Hudson-180868.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=675&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=max&amp;enlarge=true\" alt=\"Kate Hudson reveals how she landed Penny Lane in Almost Famous after nearly  playing another role\" \u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp class=\"center\"\u003EImage Courtesy: Cinema Express\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cdiv type=\"dfp\" position=2\u003EAd2\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIn current times, Hudson's portrayal of Penny Lane is regarded as one of the most recognizable in contemporary cinema. In recent comments, Hudson disclosed that Sarah Polley was originally cast to play Penny and that she had originally been assigned the minor role of Anita, which ultimately went to Zooey Deschanel. Crowe offered her the role after four auditions after Hudson asked her directly if she could try out for Penny Lane after Polley and others left. Her life was transformed by that moment; she was nominated for an Academy Award, won a Golden Globe, and solidified her reputation in Hollywood.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Ch2\u003EFrom Anita to Penny Lane: The Turning Point\u003C\u002Fh2\u003E\u003Cp\u003EKate Hudson recently told to Entertainment Tonight, how she was originally cast as Anita, a supporting role, in 'Almost Famous,' while Sarah Polley was set to play Penny Lane and Brad Pitt was to take on the role of Russell Hammond. When Polley and others exited the project, Hudson seized the moment: \"Cameron, can I please audition for Penny Lane?\" she asked.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic-gi.asianetnews.com\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fpost_attachments\u002Fimages\u002FM\u002FMV5BMTY0MzNmMjgtYzg4Yy00NGQ5LWFjYzMtNzU3MzVlZTg3YWZlXkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_-803271.jpg\" alt=\"Kate Hudson Used 'An Amalgamation Of Different Women' To Inspire Penny Lane  In Almost Famous - IMDb\" \u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cdiv type=\"dfp\" position=3\u003EAd3\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\u003Cp class=\"center\"\u003EImage Courtesy: IMDb\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlthough Crowe was hesitant at first, Hudson's passion and determination convinced him to let her try. After four auditions, she finally got the call. Hudson described the moment she learned she was cast: pure disbelief and joy. She has called it a transformative point in her life, saying the role \"completely changed my life. It changed the whole trajectory of my career.\"\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso Read: \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Findigomusic.com\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fnicole-kidman-confirms-practical-magic-2-has-wrapped-filmingsequel-arrives-september-2026-10465717\" title=\"Also Read: \" rel=\"dofollow\"\u003Ehttps:\u002F\u002Findigomusic.com\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fnicole-kidman-confirms-practical-magic-2-has-wrapped-filmingsequel-arrives-september-2026-10465717\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cdiv type=\"dfp\" position=4\u003EAd4\u003C\u002Fdiv\u003E\u003Ch2\u003EWhat She's Up To Now &amp; Legacy of Penny Lane\u003C\u002Fh2\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETwo and a half decades after 'Almost Famous,' Kate Hudson reflects on Penny Lane's legacy with warmth and gratitude. In addition to her fame as an actress, the movie helped her break into music, which culminated in her first album, 'Glorious,' in which she even drew inspiration from the musical essence of her Penny Lane role. She also stared in the Netflix comedy series 'Running Point,' where she plays Isla Gordon, who is unpredictably promoted to head of her family's professional basketball team.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\"kate-hudson-hugh-jackman-song-sung-blue-042225-3a42610e6c394bdda0a21c060f5a7fbd\" src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic-gi.asianetnews.com\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F09\u002F15\u002Fkate-hudson-hugh-jackman-song-sung-blue-042225-3a42610e6c394bdda0a21c060f5a7fbd-2025-09-15-15-05-50.jpg\" \u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp class=\"center\"\u003EImage Courtesy: People\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELater this year, 'Song Sung Blue,' a musical drama starring Hugh Jackman, is also to be released. Hudson claims that, like the movie that made Penny Lane famous, she still pursues endeavours that combine her love of music, acting, and moving narrative.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlso Read: \u003Ca href=\"https:\u002F\u002Findigomusic.com\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fbenicio-del-toro-reflects-on-sharing-the-screen-with-leonardo-dicaprio-in-one-battle-after-another-10465621\" title=\"Also Read: \" rel=\"dofollow\"\u003Ehttps:\u002F\u002Findigomusic.com\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fbenicio-del-toro-reflects-on-sharing-the-screen-with-leonardo-dicaprio-in-one-battle-after-another-10465621\u003C\u002Fa\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","headline":"Kate Hudson Reveals How She Fought to Play Penny Lane in 'Almost Famous'","summary":"In a recent interview marking Almost Famous's 25th anniversary, Kate Hudson shared she was originally cast as Anita before persuading director Cameron Crowe to let her audition for Penny Lane. ","publishedAt":1757929113564,"initialPublishedDate":1757929113564,"relativeURL":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fkate-hudson-reveals-how-she-fought-to-play-penny-lane-in-almost-famous-10466008","keywords":[{"displayName":"Kate Hudson","link":"\u002Ftag\u002Fkate-hudson"},{"displayName":"Almost Famous","link":"\u002Ftag\u002Falmost-famous"},{"displayName":"Penny Lane","link":"\u002Ftag\u002Fpenny-lane"}],"status":"PUBLISHED","updatedAt":1757929113564,"leadImage":{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F09\u002F15\u002Funtitled-design-2025-09-15-15-00-38.png","credit":"","caption":"","altText":null,"coordinates16x9":null,"coordinates1x1":null,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer16x9":true},"nextInQueue":[{"id":"5sp7s0g","headline":"Emmy Awards 2025: Full List of Winners","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Femmy-awards-2025-full-list-of-winners-10465416","imageURL":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F09\u002F15\u002Femmy-2025-2025-09-15-11-47-58.png"},{"id":"avq3nz8","headline":"Jenna Ortega Stuns in Jewel-Encrusted Top at 2025 Emmys","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fjenna-ortega-stuns-in-jewel-encrusted-top-at-2025-emmys-10465670","imageURL":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F09\u002F15\u002Ffeature-jenna-ortega-2025-09-15-12-27-07.png"},{"id":"h2ft5e9","headline":"Nicole Kidman Confirms 'Practical Magic 2' Has Wrapped Filming—Sequel Arrives September 2026","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fnicole-kidman-confirms-practical-magic-2-has-wrapped-filmingsequel-arrives-september-2026-10465717","imageURL":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F09\u002F15\u002Funtitled-design-2025-09-15-13-01-08.png"},{"id":"fc2az1o","headline":"Benicio Del Toro Reflects on Sharing the Screen with Leonardo DiCaprio in 'One Battle After Another'","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fbenicio-del-toro-reflects-on-sharing-the-screen-with-leonardo-dicaprio-in-one-battle-after-another-10465621","imageURL":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F09\u002F15\u002Funtitled-design-del-2025-09-15-11-58-56.png"},{"id":"b928wd0","headline":"Ego Nwodim Bids Farewell to 'SNL' After Seven Hilarious Seasons","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fego-nwodim-bids-farewell-to-snl-after-seven-hilarious-seasons-10465568","imageURL":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F09\u002F15\u002Funtitled-design-ego-2025-09-15-11-41-52.png"}],"recommended":[{"articleId":"1pf3x9u","headline":"Sharon D Clarke Makes History in RSC's New 'Othello' Reimagining","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fsharon-d-clarke-makes-history-in-rscs-new-othello-reimagining-articleshow-1pf3x9u","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kwhc1hj7bnqc6qxqrags65fe\u002Fcopy-of-untitled-1782994486855.png","publishedDate":1782996269688,"description":"\u003Cp\u003ESharon D Clarke is set to make Royal Shakespeare Company history as its first Black lesbian Othello in a groundbreaking reinterpretation of Shakespeare's tragedy. Set in a climate-threatened future, the production opens on 13th February, 2027, promising a bold new take on race, gender and power.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jul 02 2026, 06:14 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"1,0,1278,719","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"isSeoRequired":0,"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782996269693,"wordCount":531},{"articleId":"645vmd5","headline":"Lionel Messi Joins Tom Holland in 'Spider-Man: Brand New Day' Promo","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Flionel-messi-joins-tom-holland-in-spider-man-brand-new-day-promo-articleshow-645vmd5","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kwenj721twtmvzv6wcfffbj0\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--72--1782903807040.png","publishedDate":1782904072196,"description":"\u003Cp\u003ELionel Messi's surprise appearance alongside Tom Holland in a 'Spider-Man: Brand New Day' promotional video has become one of 2026's biggest viral entertainment moments. The unexpected crossover is boosting anticipation for the Marvel film, which arrives in theaters on 31st July, with Tom Holland returning as Peter Parker.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jul 01 2026, 04:37 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"isSeoRequired":0,"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782904072201,"wordCount":636},{"articleId":"umomypx","headline":"2026 BET Awards Winners List: Teyana Taylor Sweeps Big, Lauryn Hill Makes History","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002F2026-bet-awards-winners-list-teyana-taylor-sweeps-big-lauryn-hill-makes-history-articleshow-umomypx","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kwc6xajhsh25zcmwk5qh9k3b\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--71--1782821333585.png","publishedDate":1782822705991,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EThe 2026 BET Awards saw Teyana Taylor dominate with four major wins, while Lauryn Hill made history by receiving the inaugural Living Legend Icon Award. Hosted by Druski in Los Angeles, the ceremony also celebrated top winners including Clipse, Cardi B, Kendrick Lamar, Kehlani, and Michael B. Jordan.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 30 2026, 06:01 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"isSeoRequired":0,"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782822705996,"wordCount":501},{"articleId":"gq57146","headline":"Amid 'MobLand' Controversy, Tom Hardy Announces 'Czarface Meets Frankie Pulitzer' Rap Album","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Famid-mobland-controversy-tom-hardy-announces-czarface-meets-frankie-pulitzer-rap-album-articleshow-gq57146","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kw9p6m7bw5xcd2cetzj6bny0\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--70--1782736703723.png","publishedDate":1782737564307,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EHollywood star Tom Hardy makes a surprise return to his underground hip-hop roots, announcing an all-star collaborative rap album with Czarface and Busta Rhymes scheduled for an August release.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 29 2026, 06:22 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"isSeoRequired":0,"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782737564312,"wordCount":632},{"articleId":"kpw8psd","headline":"After 9 Years, Paul Wesley & Nina Dobrev Are Back Together for Hulu's 'You Deserve to Know'","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news\u002Fafter-9-years-paul-wesley-and-nina-dobrev-are-back-together-for-hulu-you-deserve-to-know-articleshow-kpw8psd","type":"ARTICLE","imageURL":"\u002Fimages\u002F01kw9nnbrwpn84k2wpzp3ep65t\u002Fcopy-of-untitled--69--1782736138012.png","publishedDate":1782736160361,"description":"\u003Cp\u003EPaul Wesley and Nina Dobrev are reuniting as both stars and executive producers for Hulu's 'You Deserve to Know,' based on Aggie Blum Thompson's bestselling 2025 novel. The long-awaited collaboration marks their first major scripted project together since 'The Vampire Diaries' ended in 2017.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","stats":"","readableDate":"Jun 29 2026, 05:59 PM IST","coordinates16x9":"0,0,1280,720","coordinates1x1":"280,0,720,720","fitToContainer16x9":true,"fitToContainer1x1":true,"fitToContainer3x4":false,"categoryName":"Pop News","author":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"isSeoRequired":0,"categoryUrl":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news","updatedAt":1782736160365,"wordCount":779}],"nextTenArticles":["5sp7s0g","avq3nz8","h2ft5e9","fc2az1o","b928wd0"],"breadCrumb":[{"displayName":"Pop News","link":"\u002Fpop-cultures\u002Fwhats-up-pop-news"},{"displayName":"Kate Hudson Reveals How She Fought to Play Penny Lane in 'Almost Famous'"}],"author":{"displayName":"Ankita Banerjee","link":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee","bio":"Explore the latest stories from Ankita Banerjee on indigomusic u2013 your go-to destination for music, artist, and entertainment stories.","imageUrl":"https:\u002F\u002Fstatic-gcp.asianetnews.com\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fagency_attachments\u002F2025\u002F10\u002F31\u002F2025-10-31t105753691z-web-banner-logo-_blue-background-2025-10-31-16-27-53.png","id":"91840"},"author1":{},"source":"","totalCount":0,"pageNo":0,"readableDate":"Sep 15 2025, 03:08 PM IST","contentType":"ARTICLE","articleAuthor":{"authorId":"91840","name":"Ankita Banerjee","url":"\u002Fauthor\u002Fankita-banerjee"},"createdAt":1757929113564,"breadCrumbName":"Pop News","language":"indigomusic","readableInitialPublishedDate":"Sep 15 2025, 03:08 PM IST","isSeoRequired":0,"translatedContent":false,"isExclusiveContent":false,"isOriginal":false,"isEvergreen":false,"isBreakingNews":false,"generateBodyAudioUrl":false,"storyDescription":"Pop News: Explore the latest pop news, trending music updates, artist stories, celebrity buzz, album releases, and entertainment news only at Indigomusic."},"nextArticles":{"fetched":false,"items":""}},"hasError":false},"photoshow":{"data":{"galleries":[{"id":"vuywzfc","categoryId":140005,"categoryName":"Photos","seo":{"keywords":["film"],"newsKeywords":["film"],"title":"Movies To Watch 'If You Love It Ends With Us'","description":"Love 'It Ends With Us'? Here are 10 emotional, romantic, and thought-provoking films that explore love, healing, and self-discovery in powerful ways.\n","canonical":"\u002Fcelebrity-outfits\u002Fmovies-to-watch-if-you-love-it-ends-with-us-9530061","ogTitle":"Movies To Watch 'If You Love It Ends With Us'","ogDescription":"Fans of 'It Ends With Us' will love these 10 emotional films exploring romance, trauma, healing, and self-discovery—each echoing the novel’s powerful themes and heartfelt storytelling.","ogImage":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Flove-story-2025-07-24-11-47-44.png","noindex":false},"images":[{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Fblue-valentine-2025-07-24-11-32-14.jpg","headline":"Blue Valentine ","description":"This raw, unfiltered look at a deteriorating relationship is both heartbreaking and beautifully acted. Like 'It Ends With Us', it examines how love can be both a saving grace and a source of pain.","credit":"imdb"},{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F06\u002F05\u002Fthe-notebook-feature-731686.png","headline":"The Notebook","description":"Based on Nicholas Sparks’ novel, this film explores the lasting power of love amidst obstacles like memory loss, societal expectations, and time—perfect for fans of Hoover’s deeply emotional storytelling.","credit":"IMDb"},{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Fmarriage-story-2025-07-24-11-34-22.jpg","headline":"Marriage Story ","description":"A brutally honest portrayal of love’s unravelling, this film resonates with those drawn to the realistic and painful dynamics between Lily, Ryle, and Atlas.","credit":"netflix"},{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Fsafe-haven-2025-07-24-11-35-35.jpg","headline":"Safe Haven ","description":"Another Nicholas Sparks adaptation, the film follows a woman fleeing an abusive relationship who finds hope and healing in a small town. Echoes of Lily’s journey are strong here.","credit":"imdb"},{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Fthe-vow-2025-07-24-11-36-36.jpg","headline":"The Vow ","description":"A romantic drama that explores the themes of memory, identity, and whether love can survive life-altering circumstances—mirroring the emotional pull of 'It Ends With Us'.","credit":"imdb"},{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Fpieces-of-a-woman-2025-07-24-11-37-25.jpg","headline":"Pieces of a Woman","description":"While more focused on grief than romance, this film’s emotional intensity and focus on a woman’s resilience in the face of unimaginable loss will resonate with Hoover fans.","credit":"imdb"},{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Frevolutionary-road-2025-07-24-11-38-20.jpg","headline":"Revolutionary Road ","description":"This devastating exploration of a crumbling marriage delves into the cost of suppressed dreams and societal pressures—offering another lens on painful but necessary emotional growth.","credit":"netflix"},{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Fbefore-we-go-2025-07-24-11-39-40.jpg","headline":"Before We Go","description":"A quiet, introspective story of two strangers finding connection over one night in New York City. It’s emotional, sincere, and offers the kind of soul-searching introspection that fans of 'It Ends With Us' will appreciate.","credit":"imdb"},{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Fa-star-is-born-2025-07-24-11-40-40.jpg","headline":"A Star Is Born","description":"Love, addiction, sacrifice, and personal growth are front and centre in this tragic romance. The emotional highs and lows mirror the turmoil Lily experiences in her relationships.","credit":"imdb"},{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Fme-before-you-2025-07-24-11-41-40.jpg","headline":"Me Before You","description":"A romance built on emotional vulnerability, this film also explores the ethics of choice, personal growth, and letting go—all key themes in 'It Ends With Us'.","credit":"prime video"}],"headline":"Movies To Watch 'If You Love It Ends With Us'","summary":"Fans of 'It Ends With Us' will love these 10 emotional films exploring romance, trauma, healing, and self-discovery—each echoing the novel’s powerful themes and heartfelt storytelling.\n","publishedAt":1753685918203,"initialPublishedDate":1753685918203,"relativeURL":"\u002Fcelebrity-outfits\u002Fmovies-to-watch-if-you-love-it-ends-with-us-9530061","keywords":[{"displayName":"film","link":"\u002Ftag\u002Ffilm"}],"status":"PUBLISHED","updatedAt":1753685918203,"leadImage":{"url":"\u002Findigomusic\u002Fmedia\u002Fmedia_files\u002F2025\u002F07\u002F24\u002Flove-story-2025-07-24-11-47-44.png","credit":"","caption":"","altText":null,"coordinates16x9":null,"coordinates1x